'''Terril Naval Base''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] installation located in the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[New Calamar]] on [[Esseles/Legends|Esseles's]] [[Esseles's southern continent|southern continent]]. 10 [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyers]] were assigned to the base. Prior to the Imperial occupation, a [[Jedi chapter house (Esseles)|Jedi chapter house]] was located on the site.<ref name="CatCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

